  "text": "These sequences are used to increase conspicuity of a renal mass, and to depict the renal arteries and veins, for the evaluation of the extent of the tumor in the perinephric fat and the relationship of a renal tumor to the hilar vessels and collecting system, which is helpful to the urologist in surgical planning [CITATION_1] .",
